'''2015年阿克拉加油站爆炸火災'''，是指發生於當地時間2015年6月3日晚，於[[西非|西非]]國家[[加纳|加纳]]首都[[阿克拉|阿克拉]]的一起爆炸火災。當地的一座[[加油站|加油站]]發生了大[[爆炸|爆炸]]而導致火災。當地消防局在晚上9時45分接到火警通報，而大火延燒至4日清晨4時後才撲滅，也連帶燒毀了加油站附近的幾間[[平房|平房]]<ref name=xinhuanet />。死亡人數超過百人，而消防局長證實的死亡人數為96人，受傷人數以及事故原因有待進一步調查<ref name=xinhuanet>{{cite news|author1=林晓蔚|title=加纳加油站大火死亡人数已过百|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-06/04/c_1115517405.htm|accessdate=2015-06-04|agency=[[新華社|新華社]]|date=2015-06-04|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008035043/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-06/04/c_1115517405.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
{{main|2015年阿克拉洪災}}
2015年6月1日起，當地開始下起連續數日的[[暴雨|暴雨]]<ref name="dailyguideghana2">{{cite web | url=http://www.dailyguideghana.com/rains-wash-accra/ | title=Rains Wash Accra | publisher=[[Daily_Guide|Daily Guide]] | date=3 June 2015 | accessdate=4 June 2015 | author=Gomda, A.R. | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706201925/http://www.dailyguideghana.com/rains-wash-accra/ | archivedate=2015年7月6日 }}</ref>，其結果導致了{{link-en|2015年阿克拉洪災|2015 Accra floods|洪災}}的發生，市區內的[[交通|交通]]陷入癱瘓，[[市場|市場]]交易與[[工業|工業]]生產也因[[工人|工人]]們受困而被迫停擺<ref name="gbcghana1">{{cite web | url=http://gbcghana.com/1.4206905 | title=Accra flooded following continuous Rainfall | publisher=gbcghana.com | date=2 June 2015 | accessdate=4 June 2015 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150605001927/http://gbcghana.com/1.4206905 | archivedate=2015年6月5日 }}</ref><ref name="citi1">{{cite web | url=http://citifmonline.com/2015/06/03/floods-submerge-accra-for-the-umpteenth-time/ | title=Floods submerge Accra for the umpteenth time | publisher=citifmonline.com | date=3 June 2015 | accessdate=4 June 2015 | archive-date=2015-06-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604203150/http://citifmonline.com/2015/06/03/floods-submerge-accra-for-the-umpteenth-time/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。事發前，由於一場大雨，有數以百計的民眾跑到加油站躲雨<ref name=cna>{{cite news|title=迦納加油站火災70多人致死 恐續增|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201506040356-1.aspx|accessdate=2015-06-04|agency=[[中央社|中央社]]|date=2015-06-04|archive-date=2015-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150605001925/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201506040356-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 火災 ==
6月3日，鄰近{{link-en|恩克魯瑪交流道|Kwame Nkrumah Interchange}}，{{link-en|迦納石油公司|Ghana Oil Company}}（GOIL）所擁有的一座加油站發生火災<ref name="graph2">{{cite web | url=http://www.graphic.com.gh/news/general-news/44119-disaster-many-dead-in-fuel-station-fire.html | title=UPDATE: Disaster! Many dead in fuel station fire | publisher=www.graphic.com.gh | date=4 June 2015 | accessdate=4 June 2015 | author=Baiocchi, Francisco | archive-date=2015-06-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604184134/http://www.graphic.com.gh/news/general-news/44119-disaster-many-dead-in-fuel-station-fire.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，火災也燒毀了附近的「迦納商業銀行」（Ghana Commercial Bank）<ref name="Albert Benefo Buabeng" />，以及一間[[藥局|藥局]]<ref name="peacefmonline1">{{cite web | url=http://news.peacefmonline.com/pages/social/201506/243875.php | title=Accra Floods: Over 80 People Dead In Goil Filling Station Fire | publisher=peacefmonline.com | date=4 June 2015 | accessdate=4 June 2015 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604222557/http://news.peacefmonline.com/pages/social/201506/243875.php | archivedate=2015年6月4日 }}</ref>。

== 善後 ==
超過100名的死者與其他傷者都被轉送到{{link-en|37軍醫院|37 Military Hospital}}，不過醫院很快就宣布，他們已經無法再接收更多的患者<ref name="dailyguide1">{{cite web | url=http://www.dailyguideghana.com/accra-floods-more-than-100-feared-dead-after-explosion/ | title=Accra floods: More than 100 feared dead after explosion | publisher=[[Daily_Guide|Daily Guide]] | date=4 June 2015 | accessdate=4 June 2015 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707115044/http://www.dailyguideghana.com/accra-floods-more-than-100-feared-dead-after-explosion/ | archivedate=2015年7月7日 }}</ref><ref name="indp">{{cite web | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/accra-floods-more-than-70-people-reported-dead-after-petrol-station-fire-in-ghanas-capital-city-10296123.html | title=Accra floods: More than 70 people reported dead after petrol station fire in Ghana's capital city | publisher=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] | date=4 June 2015 | accessdate=4 June 2015 | author=O'Connor, Roisin | archive-date=2019-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912070042/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/accra-floods-scores-of-people-dead-after-petrol-station-fire-in-ghanas-capital-city-10296123.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月4日晚，當局稱死者已超過了200人，衛生部長Alex Segbefia表示，他去醫院訪視過後，看到傷者們有著不同程度的[[燒傷|燒傷]]，他也呼籲迦納人緊急[[捐血|捐血]]，因為突然湧入的大量傷患，使得醫院血庫的存量嚴重不足，死亡人數可能還要再增加<ref name="Albert Benefo Buabeng" />。

